Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类因人口膨胀而向宇宙移民已过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周围漂浮着巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的“第二故乡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就在这里出生、成长、生儿育女\N并走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.71,0:02:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘卡尔玛之死’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.79,0:03:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问你父亲打算何时会到地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没听他说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若他来的话,可以介绍我认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！卡尔玛上校真英俊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.75,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.71,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很英俊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最讨厌便是这类人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若他们知道有White Base这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能会吓一跳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.83,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们要加强监视，我要夺取那艘联邦军舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛，那边的绅士是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有用得上我的话随便说吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是前市长 艾森威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很憎恨ZION国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但为了保护市民，所以留在此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来他很顽固呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾森威先生的千金依榭莲娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我失陪一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在最前线仍要说恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛真是大少爷脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION国最高统帅的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸是否不愿意将你嫁给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也猜到你爸爸会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说，ZION和联邦也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛就是卡尔玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就只爱你一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我宁可离开爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我却不可背叛我爸爸和ZION国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.81,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在有个可取得联邦军机密的大好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果成功的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲也会答应我的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果到时爸爸还不允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要离开ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，说吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那艘木马已进入S.3地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.37,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果给他闯过了这条防线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马就会进入联邦军的范围了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.65,0:05:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好我已早有准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.31,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待会将特别机动队调去那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并通知夏亚少校准备出战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我夺取到联邦的新武器后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会送它回国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时你和我一起去好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.71,0:06:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看ZION军不会让我们离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...我们怎办好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，不如由我用调虎离山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.94,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引他们到别处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，这是没用的，而且已太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到雷达讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有大批战机正从北面过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有战斗空母吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎只有一架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有战机吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来调虎离山计更有必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,？？作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时White Base就可以走到海面那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.54,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！想调虎离山或想强行突破也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是照明弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面是不是乌天尼亚球场？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！是一个球场！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极！将母舰收藏到里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该够进入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量防止敌军发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先将所有引擎的热源关掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后趁敌军不察觉就尽快冲出重围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，我反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你去GUNDAM里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯去钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良、隼人就到钢坦克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.53,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别忘了母舰内仍有大量平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实...我也只是平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它人到战斗岗位侯命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等候我的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别发出任何声音，知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位听着，别离开自己房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,180度转向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！180度转向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无路可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没法子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正要死...我要落地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，逃入市区便成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，别灰心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大家一起同心协力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.86,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.98,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你不好，吓坏他了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底你们在干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，让我来抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖...别吵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BB...BB啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我刚背过身就看不到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BB，你没事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到现在仍未有线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未找到那艘木马战舰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们仍未离开的，继续找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想令躲起来的家伙走出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好就是采用密集了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.79,0:10:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！叫他们向地面进行密集轰炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样也炸不中的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得庆祝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐要出去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，你现在出去便会白白送死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.84,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你父亲快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们怎可这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.74,0:11:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有地方要去，放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和爸爸已经无话可说了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说ZION国王儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想娶你做皇妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别以为你是我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可干涉我的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有权选择自己喜欢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不准许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.47,0:12:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喷射机的钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不可交给小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！\N知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样，木马出来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，暂时未有发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底在那里？为何发现不到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照形势来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班人已经愈来愈懂得怎样交战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我唯有亲自下去找找看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.15,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，如果需要的话我和部下去便足够了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愿意帮我忙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.99,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当然愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是你部下啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然现在是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但本来你是我二哥的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你比平时紧张得多呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别要因为女孩子而急于立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要镇定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你全权处理吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟说我为了依榭莲娜而急于立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是相当冷静的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.35,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现他们要立即通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我打败他们给你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.19,0:13:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你专诚来送我真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有这个打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了，卡尔玛上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了，夏亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜利的荣耀是属于你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，有3台机动战士下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还正向我们这边来呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！阿姆罗，听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快让GUNDAM出去应战吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用刚才你说的战术去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去引开ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好把敌人本队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以引他们来母舰的前方吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后由母舰作主力攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.47,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢加农准备待命出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去那边看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得利用自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是太好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马那边好像有机动战士来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被发现了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.49,0:15:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在附近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来会危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士的动作愈来愈灵活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一手呢，机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎想叫我到别的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.13,0:17:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦即是说，木马在后面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们真想得周到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要报这个仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等你很久了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士想逃走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰应在前面，追着它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开激光炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部准备开火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，敌军向前飞去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，米莱，回岗位吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.18,0:17:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要开始攻击了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克，钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,及母舰内各炮位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡乌无防备背向着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十秒后开始发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10...9...8...7...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,6...5...4...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3...2...1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敌机在后面攻击我们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.28,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是木马！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马在后面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上升！上升啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.28,0:18:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,180度回转吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和木马同归于尽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就去诅咒你天生的不幸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？天生的不幸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！原来你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你是个好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但却是你父亲不好啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏...夏亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你暗算我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.14,0:19:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是萨比家的男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不会白白送死的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军卡乌正面飞过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.38,0:20:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是敢死队？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，快向上升，向上升！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急向上升！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体人员伏下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国荣耀长在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我们得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突破作战成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在立即离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.95,0:21:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.83,0:21:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.21,0:21:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.16,0:21:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道...我立即回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，我明白了，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会告诉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说卡尔玛在战场战死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷...你怎可以死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.79,0:22:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.46,0:22:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个自称为ZION的宇宙都市国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在月球的另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.00,0:22:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的领袖现在所得到\N卡尔玛战死的坏消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.69,0:22:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国的国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是卡尔玛的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.17,0:23:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪金萨比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.87,0:23:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到噩耗后整个人呆了\N令牌也在使者面前掉落...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.76,0:23:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗没有结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.84,0:23:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了替卡尔玛报仇，残存部队发动了特攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.01,0:23:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和良的钢加农一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.98,0:23:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击卡乌的阿姆罗面前站着一位美少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的手枪对着阿姆罗……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.08,0:23:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 ‘伊榭莲娜的悲恋’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够存活下去吗？

